                    "text": "<b>Requirements</b> The vitalia is grabbing a creature; <b>Effect</b> The vitalia inserts some of its veins into the grabbed creature and pumps violently, rapidly exchanging the victim's blood with its own. Any <a aonid=\"46\" game-obj=\"Traits\">diseases</a> or <a aonid=\"126\" game-obj=\"Traits\">poisons</a> affecting the vitalia can be transmitted to the target creature, which must make a saving throw as though it had just been targeted with the original affliction. The inverse is true as well; the vitalia must successfully save against any diseases or poisons affecting the target or contract the affliction.",
